OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773083489
OL,3,CFamily of couple imprisoned in Iran
OL,4,Ctake campaign for their freedom to US
OL,6,FThe son of a British woman imprisoned
OL,7,Fin Iran with her partner will speak in
OL,8,FWashington next week to highlight what
OL,9,Fhe describes as a profound sense of
OL,10,Fabandonment by the UK Government.
OL,12,FLindsay and Craig Foreman, both 53,
OL,13,Fwere jailed for 10 years following
OL,14,Ftheir arrest in January 2025 while
OL,15,Ftravelling through Iran during an
OL,16,Faround-the-world trip by motorcycle.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
