PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773083489
OL,3,CFamily of couple imprisoned in Iran
OL,4,Ctake campaign for their freedom to US
OL,6,FThe couple, from East Sussex, and
OL,7,Fbeing held in Tehran's Evin prison
OL,8,Fafter they were detained and sentenced
OL,9,Fon charges of espionage, which they
OL,10,Fdeny.
OL,12,FJoe Bennett, Lindsay Foreman's son,
OL,13,Fwill address the US Capitol on March
OL,14,F12 at the Transatlantic Conference on
OL,15,FHostage-Taking and Arbitrary
OL,16,FDetention, a spokesperson for the
OL,17,Ffamily said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773083489
OL,3,CFamily of couple imprisoned in Iran
OL,4,Ctake campaign for their freedom to US
OL,6,FConditions in the prison are
OL,7,Fdeteriorating rapidly amid the ongoing
OL,8,Fconflict and prisoners fear shortages
OL,9,Fof basic food supplies, the
OL,10,Fspokesperson added.
OL,12,FAn explosion blew out the windows of
OL,13,Fthe space where Mr Foreman is being
OL,14,Fheld and sent ceiling plaster raining
OL,15,Fdown on the inmates, while Lindsay
OL,16,Fdescribed to her son how women dived
OL,17,Funder metal bunk beds for cover, the
OL,18,Ffamily spokesperson said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
