OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773083489
OL,3,CFamily of couple imprisoned in Iran
OL,4,Ctake campaign for their freedom to US
OL,6,FThey said: "The legal process has
OL,7,Feffectively collapsed. The
OL,8,FRevolutionary Courts that sentenced
OL,9,Fthe couple have themselves reportedly
OL,10,Fbeen targeted in recent airstrikes.
OL,12,F"Lindsay and Craig's state-appointed
OL,13,Flawyer has left the country, and the
OL,14,Ffamily has no clarity on whether their
OL,15,Fappeal was even successfully received
OL,16,Fbefore court systems shut down."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773083489
OL,3,CFamily of couple imprisoned in Iran
OL,4,Ctake campaign for their freedom to US
OL,6,FMr Bennett said: "The advice we
OL,7,Freceived from the Foreign Office was
OL,8,Fstandard travel advice for tourists,
OL,9,Fto carry out a risk assessment and
OL,10,Ftake shelter.
OL,12,F"That is hardly illuminating or
OL,13,Freassuring when your parents are
OL,14,Ftrapped in a prison in the middle of a
OL,15,Fwar zone."
OL,17,FMr Bennett will use his address in
OL,18,FWashington to highlight what he
OL,19,Fdescribes as a profound sense of
OL,20,Fabandonment by the UK government.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773083489
OL,3,CFamily of couple imprisoned in Iran
OL,4,Ctake campaign for their freedom to US
OL,6,FHe said: "While the Prime Minister has
OL,7,Fspoken about the regional conflict in
OL,8,FParliament, he has not once mentioned
OL,9,Fthe names of Lindsay and Craig
OL,10,FForeman, two British citizens sitting
OL,11,Fin a prison in Tehran with the skies
OL,12,Flit up by explosions.
OL,14,F"The Foreign Secretary said she would
OL,15,Fmeet with our family after the
OL,16,Fsentencing and if circumstances
OL,17,Fchanged. My parents have now been
OL,18,Fsentenced and they are being held
OL,19,Finside a prison in an active conflict
OL,20,Fzone. I would say that counts as
OL,21,Fchange.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773083489
OL,3,CFamily of couple imprisoned in Iran
OL,4,Ctake campaign for their freedom to US
OL,6,F"Neither the Prime Minister nor the
OL,7,FForeign Secretary have responded to
OL,8,Four petition delivered to Downing
OL,9,FStreet earlier this year. My letters
OL,10,Fto them have also gone unanswered.
OL,12,F"My parents are not spies. They are
OL,13,Finnocent tourists who have been taken
OL,14,Fhostage. Pretending otherwise does not
OL,15,Fmake the problem go away."
OL,17,FThe family are calling for the Foreign
OL,18,FSecretary formally to designate the
OL,19,Fcase as arbitrary detention.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
